<function>

access:  static public

name: files

param: string, $key, NULL

param: unknown, $default, array ()

return: mixed

</function>

Safely gets the value of an element from the $_FILES array.

* Parameters:

 * string //$key//: The array element; if null, returns the whole array.

 * unknown //$default//: 

* Returns mixed: The array element value (if set), or the $default value (if not).

Safely gets the value of an element from the $_FILES array.

Returns an empty array if the requested key does not exist.